~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : actions                                   ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : actions

   This shows a current list of system socials.  These are like 
   other commands.  They will act like other commands.

   NOTE:  $*  is a representations of .<command> <all other text goes in $*>
          $1  is a representation of first word after the .<command> 

